criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  signed informed consent

          -  age >=18 years;

          -  pulmonary tuberculosis defined by positive sputum microscopy (waiting for culture
             confirmation)

          -  sensitivity to first-line anti-TB drugs;

          -  normal liver and renal function.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  severe malnutrition;

          -  HIV infection
